</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="24.[160,1155,1215,1309]" pageId="24" pageNumber="1058">
<emphasis box="[160,310,1250,1274]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="1058">
Ae. 
<taxonomicName authority="Frolov &amp; Akhmetova &amp; Vaz-de-Mello, 2017" authorityName="Frolov &amp; Akhmetova &amp; Vaz-de-Mello" authorityYear="2017" box="[200,310,1250,1274]" class="Insecta" family="Hybosoridae" genus="Aegidium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="1058" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angustum" status="sp. nov.">angustum</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[317,405,1250,1274]" pageId="24" pageNumber="1058" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
can be separated from other continental members of 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Lacordaire" authorityYear="1856" box="[1017,1120,1250,1274]" class="Insecta" family="Hybosoridae" genus="Aegidium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="24" pageNumber="1058" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
